276
00:22:37,820 --> 00:22:39,587
You…

277
00:22:41,487 --> 00:22:43,520
Do you want to go to Seoul with me?

278
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:46,553
- No. 
 - Why?

279
00:22:46,553 --> 00:22:48,620
Because of Ah Reum?

280
00:22:53,687 --> 00:22:55,753
His birth wasn't registered,

281
00:22:55,753 --> 00:22:58,520
and only a note with his name and age was left.

282
00:22:59,653 --> 00:23:01,953
Just leave him to an orphanage.

283
00:23:02,787 --> 00:23:05,620
How can she abandon a child at a motel and leave?

284
00:23:08,753 --> 00:23:10,520
Well…

285
00:23:13,087 --> 00:23:15,587
In that letter…

286
00:23:17,020 --> 00:23:20,987
The letter said they would come to find the child,

287
00:23:20,987 --> 00:23:26,087
so would it be all right if I keep him for now?

288
00:23:27,020 --> 00:23:28,787
Then, please go ahead and do that.

289
00:23:32,220 --> 00:23:34,220
What's your name?

290
00:23:34,220 --> 00:23:35,920
Cha Seung Eon.

291
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:38,420
From now on, you're my sibling.

292
00:23:40,587 --> 00:23:44,253
Because my mom said she would come to get me.

293
00:23:44,253 --> 00:23:46,520
I have to wait.

294
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:50,687
But I can't remember Mom's face.

295
00:23:52,753 --> 00:23:56,020
I can't even go to look for her.

296
00:23:56,020 --> 00:23:59,553
So, I can't leave here, Kang Hee.

297
00:24:01,120 --> 00:24:03,320
You don't have a picture of your mom?

298
00:24:31,187 --> 00:24:36,553
Your mom once said that I could call her 'mom.'

299
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,253
That's right.

300
00:24:43,120 --> 00:24:48,653
My mom loved you more than me.

301
00:24:50,153 --> 00:24:51,820
I remember this day.

302
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:53,953
It was the school entrance ceremony.

303
00:24:53,953 --> 00:24:57,220
Even though it was the ceremony, Mom didn't come to school

304
00:24:57,220 --> 00:25:00,153
and instead asked to take pictures in front of the house.

305
00:25:00,787 --> 00:25:03,887
So I threw a tantrum and didn't take the picture.

306
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:12,520
I should've taken it.

307
00:25:13,453 --> 00:25:15,420
I'll give it to you.

308
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:25,087
It's yours, isn't it?

309
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:29,753
My mom's photo…

310
00:25:30,420 --> 00:25:34,987
Thank you for keeping it so long.

311
00:25:38,320 --> 00:25:40,887
And I'm sorry, Seung Eon.

312
00:26:17,220 --> 00:26:18,353
Good morning.

313
00:26:18,353 --> 00:26:20,620
- Did you sleep well? 
 - Yes.

314
00:26:20,620 --> 00:26:22,987
You were going to Seoul without even saying goodbye to me, weren't you?

315
00:26:22,987 --> 00:26:26,153
No, I was just about to go say goodbye now.

316
00:26:26,153 --> 00:26:27,853
You were?

317
00:26:31,253 --> 00:26:35,520
I didn't know the manager worked that much.

318
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:40,353
I was able to focus on the field thanks to the manager.

319
00:26:40,353 --> 00:26:42,587
Tell me honestly.

320
00:26:42,587 --> 00:26:44,253
Yes.

321
00:26:44,253 --> 00:26:48,020
Did your heart waver even a little when you were proposed to?

322
00:26:48,020 --> 00:26:50,920
Of course, it wavered.

323
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:54,587
My mental state was completely shattered.

324
00:26:54,587 --> 00:26:57,120
If you don't come quickly, I'll make a public proposal like that, too.

325
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:59,287
You think I'd be scared?

326
00:26:59,287 --> 00:27:01,620
I'll make a public proposal to you, too.

327
00:27:01,620 --> 00:27:03,520
To the whole world.

328
00:27:04,287 --> 00:27:05,887
I'm sorry.

329
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:11,453
Manager,

330
00:27:11,453 --> 00:27:15,287
do you know the orders for the sinks and sanitary ware are all wrong?

331
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:17,987
Then you do it again.

332
00:27:17,987 --> 00:27:21,853
That's your work, so you handle it.

333
00:27:21,853 --> 00:27:23,487
There are hotel suppliers, right?

334
00:27:23,487 --> 00:27:27,020
Call them all up and check for products that can meet the delivery schedule,

335
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,887
compare the specifications, make a list,

336
00:27:28,887 --> 00:27:30,653
negotiate the prices, and place the orders.

337
00:27:30,653 --> 00:27:34,753
Yes, do that, Ms. Kang Hee.

338
00:27:36,120 --> 00:27:39,620
- If it's because of the proposal… 
 - Right, the proposal.

339
00:27:40,787 --> 00:27:43,187
I did that, too.

340
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:50,420
Is it because of Esther, by any chance?

341
00:27:51,687 --> 00:27:52,853
How do you know, Ms. Kang Hee?

342
00:27:52,853 --> 00:27:54,953
How did you know, Manager?

343
00:27:54,953 --> 00:27:57,620
Something seemed off about that guy, so I did a little investigation.

344
00:27:57,620 --> 00:28:01,053
And it turns out she wasn't his cousin, but a woman he lived with.

345
00:28:01,053 --> 00:28:02,570
Then, was it all because of that,

346
00:28:02,570 --> 00:28:06,920
the silence and strange behavior when you came last time?

347
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:08,787
Is it not because I rejected your proposal?

348
00:28:08,787 --> 00:28:12,253
What's the big deal about a proposal? I can just do that again.

349
00:28:12,253 --> 00:28:15,320
You are not getting married right away either.

350
00:28:15,320 --> 00:28:17,220
Esther's even pregnant.

351
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:19,120
But even if her father is such a bastard,

352
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:22,587
I can't just tell her to raise Little Heart without a father.

353
00:28:24,087 --> 00:28:27,387
I can't say it because I'm afraid she might be shocked.

354
00:28:27,387 --> 00:28:29,587
Esther already knows everything.

355
00:28:29,587 --> 00:28:34,453
She was already shocked and saw it with her own eyes.

356
00:28:36,387 --> 00:28:39,220
Is Esther okay?

357
00:28:39,220 --> 00:28:41,187
Hey, Cheon Yeon Soo.

358
00:28:42,320 --> 00:28:43,653
Is it you?

359
00:28:43,653 --> 00:28:45,287
- It's you, right? 
 - What?

360
00:28:45,287 --> 00:28:49,120
- Were you the one who talked to Min Jung? 
 - It wasn't me.

361
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:50,287
What do you mean it wasn't?

362
00:28:50,287 --> 00:28:52,687
She called the hospital and found out my number.

363
00:28:52,687 --> 00:28:54,120
It's Ms. Yoon.

364
00:28:54,120 --> 00:28:57,320
Ms. Yoon, you took the call. Right?

365
00:28:57,320 --> 00:28:59,220
Yes, well…

366
00:28:59,220 --> 00:29:01,180
I'm sorry.

367
00:29:01,187 --> 00:29:03,787
No, it's all right.

368
00:29:07,220 --> 00:29:09,587
Would Ms. Yoon have answered the phone? Of course, it was me.

369
00:29:09,587 --> 00:29:11,653
Jeez.

370
00:29:11,653 --> 00:29:13,520
Why? What did Min Jung say?

371
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:14,653
She said she's coming.

372
00:29:14,653 --> 00:29:16,320
Really? Why?

373
00:29:16,320 --> 00:29:18,253
I don't know.

374
00:29:18,253 --> 00:29:21,487
No, what if Min Jung asks me to try again

375
00:29:21,487 --> 00:29:23,753
and go to Seoul together?

376
00:29:23,753 --> 00:29:24,887
That won't happen.

377
00:29:24,887 --> 00:29:27,520
How do you know her feelings?

378
00:29:27,520 --> 00:29:31,053
- Yeon Soo, save me, please. 
 - What can I do?

379
00:29:31,053 --> 00:29:35,853
If I go crazy and follow Min Jung to Seoul, hold me back.

380
00:29:35,853 --> 00:29:39,253
Hearing you talk about Min Jung, I miss Kang Hee.

381
00:29:39,253 --> 00:29:40,853
Kang Hee again?

382
00:29:40,853 --> 00:29:43,020
Can't you focus on me?

383
00:29:43,020 --> 00:29:45,287
Ms. Yoon, tomorrow…

384
00:29:45,287 --> 00:29:48,753
If we're not busy, can I take a break?

385
00:29:48,753 --> 00:29:52,187
Yes, there's nothing special tomorrow, yet.

386
00:29:52,187 --> 00:29:53,853
Is that so?

387
00:29:53,853 --> 00:29:57,753
Han Woo, you'll meet Min Jung and I'll go meet Kang Hee.

388
00:29:57,753 --> 00:29:59,253
Jeez, that disloyal punk.

389
00:29:59,253 --> 00:30:00,587
You were the first to sever ties, you know?

390
00:30:00,587 --> 00:30:02,253
Jeez, that grudge-holding punk.

391
00:30:02,253 --> 00:30:04,920
If things go well with Min Jung and we meet again,

392
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:07,187
we can hang out together in Seoul, maybe a double date.

393
00:30:07,187 --> 00:30:08,687
That piece of shit.

394
00:30:08,687 --> 00:30:11,653
You said Min Jung came to see Han Woo?

395
00:30:12,787 --> 00:30:14,920
Do you know her too? Min Jung?

396
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:17,220
Yeah, it's Han Woo's ex-girlfriend.

397
00:30:17,220 --> 00:30:21,220
They dated on the premise of marriage, so I've seen her a few times, too.

398
00:30:22,987 --> 00:30:24,753
Marriage…

399
00:30:25,653 --> 00:30:29,720
Senior Han Woo… How was his life in Seoul?

400
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:32,387
Because it's unimaginable.

401
00:30:32,387 --> 00:30:34,487
He was just exactly a finance guy.

402
00:30:34,487 --> 00:30:38,687
I really couldn't imagine he'd leave everything and come back.

403
00:30:38,687 --> 00:30:43,887
Then he must have made a really big decision to start the second act of his life.

404
00:30:43,887 --> 00:30:48,520
Isn't it wrong to give up impulsively?

405
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:50,087
Try to stop him, Unnie.

406
00:30:50,087 --> 00:30:55,187
No, how can I do that? Min Jung knows me, too.

407
00:30:55,187 --> 00:30:59,753
I guess they'll talk it out and sort things well.

408
00:31:02,387 --> 00:31:04,187
Still, should I give him a call

409
00:31:04,187 --> 00:31:06,253
to check if he's doing well with her?

410
00:31:17,220 --> 00:31:18,953
Hey, where are you?

411
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:39,120
   

412
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:40,920
Senior!

413
00:31:45,853 --> 00:31:47,553
I heard Chil Ddaeng is sick.

414
00:31:47,553 --> 00:31:49,253
What?

415
00:31:49,253 --> 00:31:51,287
Don't go.

416
00:31:52,387 --> 00:31:55,920
If you go to Seoul, who will take care of Chil Ddaeng?

417
00:31:58,520 --> 00:32:02,253
Ms. Yoon, I'm not going.

418
00:32:02,253 --> 00:32:04,120
Pardon?

419
00:32:07,987 --> 00:32:11,487
Aren't you the veterinarian who performed surgery on Chil Ddaeng?

420
00:32:11,487 --> 00:32:14,120
Oh, hello.

421
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:17,487
It's good to see you living well before I go.

422
00:32:17,487 --> 00:32:19,787
Take care.

423
00:32:19,787 --> 00:32:23,553
Congratulations on your marriage, sincerely.

424
00:32:24,287 --> 00:32:26,153
I'll get going.

425
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:31,740
♫  The cold winter comes  ♫

426
00:32:31,740 --> 00:32:36,360
♫  If your memory gets clearer   ♫

427
00:32:36,360 --> 00:32:39,950
♫  It's snowing again  ♫

428
00:32:39,953 --> 00:32:42,720
Let's go, you said Chil Ddaeng is very sick.

429
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,100
Yes.

430
00:32:44,100 --> 00:32:48,270
♫  The footsteps walking away from me  ♫

431
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:53,550
♫  Were erased, covered by snow  ♫

432
00:32:53,553 --> 00:32:54,887
Oh, right.

433
00:32:54,887 --> 00:32:57,520
Have you decided on a name for the donkey?

434
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:02,220
Not yet.

435
00:33:02,220 --> 00:33:04,720
Do you have anything in mind?

436
00:33:06,353 --> 00:33:08,953
Donkey, something like that?

437
00:33:08,953 --> 00:33:11,053
- I'm sorry. 
 - Well…

438
00:33:11,053 --> 00:33:13,387
But is it okay for you to come out so suddenly?

439
00:33:13,387 --> 00:33:15,153
What about the hospital?

440
00:33:15,153 --> 00:33:18,287
Yes, it's okay.

441
00:34:26,220 --> 00:34:28,887
 I lost the doll. 

442
00:34:29,853 --> 00:34:32,387
 The doll is missing. 

443
00:34:34,253 --> 00:34:36,520
 The day my mother left… 

444
00:34:42,553 --> 00:34:44,553
 My doll. 

445
00:34:46,953 --> 00:34:48,853
 Please find it for me. 

446
00:35:00,420 --> 00:35:02,353
Are you already here?

447
00:35:02,853 --> 00:35:05,020
Oh dear.

448
00:35:05,020 --> 00:35:07,587
I'm sorry I'm not Kang Hee.

449
00:35:08,287 --> 00:35:10,153
No, come in.

450
00:35:10,153 --> 00:35:11,987
Why are you flustered?

451
00:35:11,987 --> 00:35:14,053
No, I'm not.

452
00:35:15,387 --> 00:35:17,220
Take a seat.

453
00:35:20,453 --> 00:35:22,687
Oh dear.

454
00:35:26,253 --> 00:35:30,887
You were quite hurt because I opposed you being together, weren't you?

455
00:35:31,620 --> 00:35:35,053
Yes. A little bit.

456
00:35:35,053 --> 00:35:37,153
Actually…

457
00:35:37,787 --> 00:35:42,620
I opposed the two of you as Cheon Yeon Soo's father.

458
00:35:42,620 --> 00:35:45,353
You've been through a lot, haven't you?

459
00:35:45,353 --> 00:35:48,353
You should be happy.

460
00:35:48,353 --> 00:35:52,420
You ought to live your life.

461
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:54,953
As for me,

462
00:35:55,620 --> 00:35:59,020
I'm happy as long as Kang Hee is by my side.

463
00:35:59,753 --> 00:36:03,787
Kang Hee is my life, after all.

464
00:36:09,720 --> 00:36:15,053
Now, I'll talk to you as Kang Hee's father.

465
00:36:16,387 --> 00:36:19,320
If it were up to me,

466
00:36:20,453 --> 00:36:24,887
I'd ask you over and over...

467
00:36:26,487 --> 00:36:29,153
to take good care of Kang Hee.

468
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:33,687
Do you know how happy I was

469
00:36:33,687 --> 00:36:38,753
when you said you would go meet Kang Hee...

470
00:36:40,620 --> 00:36:42,920
instead of me last Christmas?

471
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:45,020
- Really? 
 - No, I'm lying.

472
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:46,820
Jeez.

473
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:54,287
Have I placed too much of a burden on you?

474
00:36:54,287 --> 00:36:57,620
No, not at all. Never.

475
00:36:59,120 --> 00:37:02,487
It seems like Kang Hee's memory is coming back.

476
00:37:02,487 --> 00:37:04,387
Yes.

477
00:37:04,387 --> 00:37:09,187
She even vaguely remembers fainting and losing consciousness as a child.

478
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:20,387
Thank you for being by her side.

479
00:37:31,153 --> 00:37:33,220
I'll get going now.

480
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:35,187
All right.

481
00:37:36,620 --> 00:37:39,120
- Get some rest. 
 - Yes.

482
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:42,387
Why is this rascal here, not even recognizing his master?

483
00:37:42,387 --> 00:37:45,787
Why are you hitting him? I'm the owner.

484
00:37:47,487 --> 00:37:50,087
Is it your son or your daughter?

485
00:38:25,120 --> 00:38:27,087
Kang Hee.

486
00:38:32,453 --> 00:38:34,553
Isn't she at home?

487
00:38:47,087 --> 00:38:51,387
   

488
00:38:58,387 --> 00:39:00,987
 Oh? Mom, you're awake. 

489
00:39:02,887 --> 00:39:04,720
 Kang Hee, bring your clothes, too. 

490
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:06,553
 Okay. 

491
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:11,220
 Mom. 

492
00:39:12,420 --> 00:39:14,320
 Here it is. 

493
00:39:16,620 --> 00:39:19,520
 Mom, where are we going? 

494
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:20,687
 California. 

495
00:39:20,687 --> 00:39:22,187
 This is California too, isn't it? 

496
00:39:22,187 --> 00:39:24,787
 Not here, but where I grew up. 

497
00:39:24,787 --> 00:39:26,187
 Is it far from here? 

498
00:39:26,187 --> 00:39:27,553
 It is far. 

499
00:39:27,553 --> 00:39:29,553
 How far is it? 

500
00:39:29,553 --> 00:39:31,687
 You'll find out when you get there. 

501
00:39:53,953 --> 00:39:55,853
 Let's go in. 

502
00:41:18,587 --> 00:41:21,287
 I love you, Kang Hee. 

503
00:42:00,020 --> 00:42:02,153
 Mom. 

504
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:49,287
 - Kang Hee. 
 - Kang Hee. 

505
00:42:49,287 --> 00:42:52,320
 - Ji Kang Hee. 
 - Ji Kang Hee. 

506
00:42:52,320 --> 00:42:53,853
 Where did she go? 

507
00:42:53,853 --> 00:42:57,720
 - Kang Hee. 
 - Kang Hee. 

508
00:42:57,720 --> 00:42:58,920
 - Kang Hee. 
 - Ji Kang Hee. 

509
00:42:58,920 --> 00:43:00,187
 Kang Hee. 

510
00:43:00,187 --> 00:43:02,387
 Ji Kang Hee. 

511
00:43:02,387 --> 00:43:04,553
 Ji Kang Hee. 

512
00:43:05,920 --> 00:43:08,053
 Kang Hee. 

513
00:43:09,820 --> 00:43:13,687
 She's here. I found Kang Hee. 

514
00:43:14,453 --> 00:43:16,853
 Come quickly. 

515
00:43:16,853 --> 00:43:19,287
 Open your eyes. 

516
00:43:21,687 --> 00:43:24,253
 Try opening your eyes. 

517
00:43:24,253 --> 00:43:26,353
 Come quickly. 

518
00:43:26,353 --> 00:43:30,553
 Kang Hee, open your eyes. 

519
00:43:30,553 --> 00:43:33,653
 Please, try opening your eyes. 

520
00:43:43,353 --> 00:43:45,553
 Mom. 

521
00:43:49,453 --> 00:43:52,653
 Mom, I'm sorry. 

522
00:44:26,387 --> 00:44:28,220
Kang Hee.

523
00:44:29,387 --> 00:44:30,930
Why are you so late?

524
00:44:30,930 --> 00:44:33,580
It's cold, and you didn't answer your phone.

525
00:44:37,453 --> 00:44:39,653
Why did you come without saying anything?

526
00:44:39,653 --> 00:44:42,287
I came out to pick you up.

527
00:44:42,287 --> 00:44:46,387
I was worried, wondering if you got lost or if something had happened.

528
00:44:49,920 --> 00:44:51,353
You just go first.

529
00:44:51,353 --> 00:44:53,553
What about you?

530
00:44:53,553 --> 00:44:55,520
Aren't you going?

531
00:45:00,587 --> 00:45:02,853
Should I sleep over then go?

532
00:45:07,353 --> 00:45:09,387
Let's break up.

533
00:45:11,820 --> 00:45:15,187
Let's break up now.

534
00:45:19,887 --> 00:45:21,653
Are you not feeling well?

535
00:45:21,653 --> 00:45:23,487
Just go.

536
00:45:24,320 --> 00:45:26,620
Kang Hee.

537
00:45:26,620 --> 00:45:28,487
Ji Kang Hee.

538
00:45:31,187 --> 00:45:33,053
Look at me.

539
00:45:37,787 --> 00:45:40,920
I don't know what's going on

540
00:45:40,920 --> 00:45:44,353
but if you need some time alone, I'll wait.

541
00:45:45,553 --> 00:45:48,553
When you want to talk about it later,

542
00:45:49,120 --> 00:45:51,187
tell me then.

