01:03:03,130 --> 01:03:06,830
 No matter how much you hide and avoid it, nothing will change.  

715
01:03:06,830 --> 01:03:09,700
  There's something I have to tell you.  

716
01:03:09,700 --> 01:03:11,210
  Thank you so much, Mom.  

717
01:03:11,210 --> 01:03:13,890
  It's okay now, right?  

718
01:03:13,890 --> 01:03:15,890
  Yeah, it's okay.  

719
01:03:15,890 --> 01:03:17,150
  The results don't look good.  

720
01:03:17,150 --> 01:03:18,280
  Are you sick?  

721
01:03:18,280 --> 01:03:19,800
  Yeah, I am.  

722
01:03:19,800 --> 01:03:22,860
  Tell me it's not because of me.  

723
01:03:22,860 --> 01:03:25,290
  Nothing's going to happen.  

